translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: どうだ、かっこいいだろう」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: How is it? Cool, right?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 真意が読めないといった風で、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: With an expression that made his true intentions unreadable,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ランはランスをしばし、じっと見た。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Ran looked closely at Rance for a moment.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「……今さらそんな事を言われて、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: ...Being told that now,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 説得力があると思うの？」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: do you think it sounds convincing?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「む。それは俺の深謀遠慮があってだな……」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Hmm. That's because of my deep strategy and foresight...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「カスタムに人類への裏切りはありえません。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: There can be no betrayal of humanity by Custom.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 話がそれだけというなら、失礼します」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: If that's all you have to say, then excuse me.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ああ、くそ。おい、待った。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Ah, damn it. Hey, wait.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: じゃあ、あと一個だけでいい、質問に答えてくれ」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Then, just one more question, please answer me.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 背を向けようとしたランを、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Ran was about to turn his back,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ランスは慌てて引き留めた。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: but Rance hurriedly stopped him.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「誰が怪しいと思う？」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Who do you think is suspicious?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ランは動きを止め、表情を崩さないまま、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Ran stopped moving, without changing his expression,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 指先で髪を弄る仕草で思案した。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: and pondered while playing with his hair with his fingertips.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ビヨンホウさんが……」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Ms. Biyonhou...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ビヨンホウって……ええと、ジフテリアか？」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Biyonhou... hmm, is that Jiphteria?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「はい。最近、カスタム軍をジフテリアと、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Yes. Recently, there have been several requests to allow Jiphteria to co-command the Custom army...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 一緒に指揮させてもらえないかと、何度か……」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: asking if they could jointly lead it...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「なんだそりゃ」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: What the heck is that?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「分かりません。怪しいかどうかも……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I don't know. I don't even know if it's suspicious...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ただ、以前はそういう申し出はありませんでした」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: It's just that such requests never came before.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ふぅむ、よし分かった。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Hmm, alright, I understand.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 後はベッドで……」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The rest can be done in bed...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「……それじゃ」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: ...Well then.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ちっ……逃げられたか……惜しかったな」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Tch... got away, huh... that was close.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: （惜しかった……かしら…………？）
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: (That was close... or was it...?)

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「どしたん？　ランス」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: What's wrong? Rance.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ランスの呼び出しで、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: At Rance's summons,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: コパ帝国都市長、コパンドン・ドットが現れた。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Copandon Dot, the mayor of the Copa Empire city, appeared.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「オホン。この軍には内通者がいる！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Ahem. There is a traitor within this army!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 愚かにも、このランス総統に逆らおう
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Foolishly, someone trying to oppose the Supreme Leader Rance!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: という手合いだ！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: That's the kind of person we're dealing with!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「まさかっ……まさか、それがウチや言うんかっ！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: No way... you mean it’s me?!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「そうだ、ネタは挙がっている！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: That's right, we have the evidence!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: さっさと吐いた方が身のためだぞ！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: You’d better confess quickly for your own sake!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「だって……あいつが……あいつが悪いねん！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Because... that guy... that guy is at fault!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: たこやき焼きのたこやきだけ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: He ate all the takoyaki from the takoyaki maker,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 全部つまみ食いしよって……許せんかったんや！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: snacking on them all... I couldn't forgive him!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「それでこんな事をしたのか……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: So that's why you did such a thing...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 哀しい事件だった……」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: What a sad incident...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「うっ、うっ、刑事はん……うち……うち……」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Sob, sob, officer... I... I...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「……………って、何をやらせるか！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: ...What on earth are you making me do!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「なんや暇で遊びたいんかと思って」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I thought you just wanted to play because you're bored.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「内通者がいるって話だっただろーが。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: We were talking about a traitor, weren't we?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: それを俺様が見つけてやろうというのだ」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: And I'm the one who's going to find them.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「へ？　それ、ウチを疑ってるん？」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Huh? Are you suspecting me then?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「…………考えてみたら、無いか」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: ...Now that I think about it, probably not.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「だって……あいつが……あいつが悪いねん！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Because... that guy... that guy is at fault!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: たこやき焼きのたこやきだけ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: He ate all the takoyaki from the takoyaki maker,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 全部つまみ食いしよって……許せんかったんや！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: snacking on them all... I couldn't forgive him!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「それでこんな事をしたのか……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: So that's why you did such a thing...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 哀しい事件だった……」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: What a sad incident...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「うっ、うっ、刑事はん……うち……うち……」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Sob, sob, officer... I... I...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「……………って、何をやらせるか！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: ...What on earth are you making me do!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「なんや暇で遊びたいんかと思って」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I thought you just wanted to play because you're bored.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「内通者がいるって話だっただろーが。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: We were talking about a traitor, weren't we?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: それを俺様が見つけてやろうというのだ」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: And I'm the one who's going to find them.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「へ？　それ、ウチを疑ってるん？」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Huh? Are you suspecting me then?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「…………考えてみたら、無いか」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: ...Now that I think about it, probably not.
